Description: Strathberry East/West bag handcrafted in calf leather with the iconic branded metal bar on the front. Flap with magnetic closure, gold-tone logo print on the front, sliding double-handle tubular chain shoulder strap that can be worn by hand, on the shoulder or crossbody. Interior lined in suede microfiber with a flat pocket and two compartments, gold-tone metal hardware.
Tags: Woman > Bags > Crossbody and Shoulder bags

Description: Roger Vivier mini crossbody bag made of leather with iconic Viv' Choc applique buckle on the flap. Magnetic closure, lined interior with one credit card slot, additional rear zipper pocket, and adjustable, detachable shoulder strap. Palladium-finished metalware.

Medium tote bag by Ganni made of faux leather with embossed lettering logo and contrast stitching. Double handles, magnetic closure and lined interior with one zippered pocket. Accessorized with adjustable and removable shoulder straps. Silver-finished metalware.

Mini Love Click bag by Pinko crafted in nappa leather with chevron quilting and characterized by the front flap with rounded cut-out enriched by the iconic metal Love Birds buckle with engraved logo. Magnetic closure and chain shoulder strap with adjustable leather insert. Interior lined in microfiber suede with a flat leather pocket and two compartments divided by a central zip pocket. Antique gold finished metalware.

Description: Longchamp bucket bag crafted in Cuir de Russie with single top handle, debossed logo on front and gold-tone metal logoed press-stud closure. Suede interior with a leather patch pocket.

The Hector bag by Thom Browne is made of garnet leather and features a chain strap decorated with a tricolor grosgrain ribbon. It has a zip closure and the iconic tricolor ribbon insert on the back. The interior is lined with tricolor striped fabric and includes an open flat pocket. The metallic accessories have a gold finish.

Description: The Jacquard Medium Tote Bag by Marc Jacobs in cotton-blend canvas, featuring double top handle, adjustable and removable shoulder strap, front contrasting jacquard logo, rear fabric logo patch, zip closure and side handle. Unlined interior with two open pockets and a zippered one. Silver-finished metalware.

The Leather Mini Tote Bag by Marc Jacobs crafted in grained leather with contrasting lettering logo printed on the front. Double handles, detachable and adjustable shoulder strap, side handle and zipper closure. Unlined interior and gold-tone metalware.

The Small Tote bag by Marc Jacobs in cotton canvas, featuring contrasting, adjustable, and removable webbing strap, contrasting front logo print, back logo patch, zip closure, side handle. Unlined interior. SIlver-finished metalware.

The Canvas Medium Tote Bag by Marc Jacobs made cotton fabric with detacheble and adjustable fabric shoulder strap. Contrasting lettering logo on the front, top zip closure and side handle. Unlined interior with two open pockets and a zippered one, steel-tone metalware.

The Small Tote bag by Marc Jacobs in cotton canvas, featuring contrasting, adjustable, and removable webbing strap, contrasting front logo print, back logo patch, zip closure, side handle. Unlined interior. SIlver-finished metalware.

The Jacquard Medium Tote Bag by Marc Jacobs in cotton-blend canvas, featuring double top handle, adjustable and removable shoulder strap, front contrasting jacquard logo, rear fabric logo patch, zip closure and side handle. Unlined interior with two open pockets and a zippered one. Silver-finished metalware.

The Large Traveler Tote bag by Marc Jacobs made from cotton canvas with double handle to carry by hand or on the shoulder. Contrasting logo print on front, logo patch on the back, top zip closure and side handle. Unlined interior with one zip pocket and two small pockets.

This A.P.C. open-top shopping bag is crafted of sturdy cotton canvas to a vertical silhouette with twin handles. The adjustable shoulder strap also makes it a versatile hands-free option. Signed with a front logo print, it is finished with two internal zip pockets.

Classic Love Icon Simply bag by Pinko crafted in smooth calf leather and characterized by the front flap with Love Birds metal buckle and rounded studs. Removable and adjustable leather shoulder strap with side chain inserts, joint closure and Birds embroidery on the back. Interior lined in suede microfibre with one leather flat pocket and two compartments divided by a middle zipped pocket. Antique gold finish metalware.

Description: This Marc Jacobs pouch is made of hammered leather with an embossed logo lettering. It features a zip closure, a lined interior with three credit card slots, and a removable wrist strap. The metallic accessories have a palladium finish.

This tote bag is made of a cotton blend with the iconic Burberry Check motif in jacquard. It comes with an adjustable shoulder strap featuring B-shaped buckles. The front and back have two large pockets with flaps and an adjustable side belt. The interior is lined with a cotton blend and has a zip pocket and a fabric patch decorated with the Equestrian Knight Design. The metal accessories are brushed for a sleek finish.
The Ninon tote bag by A.P.C. is made of faux leather with a contrasting printed logo lettering on the front. It features double handles and a fabric interior with an open pocket.
